<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Zal Mangpha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leisiet guol ngaih gi bang kikhenna din.
 Kawlah ni a suok kit tai zal mangpha (2)

[V2]
 2. Nuoi simlei ahin lungmuonna umlo
 Lungngaihna meipi'n ei bawm ki ging un (2)

[V3]
 3. Ni khat nawpna zai... la sa mah leu hing
 Pak thing lun a muol bang in, a muol hi (2)

[V4]
 4. Gi bang kikhen ding nuoi simlei a ngui
 Lunghelna khawvui a kai, chieh tauin. (2)

[V5]
 5. Chung thangvan kikhen umlohna gamah,
 Luontui bang kigawm naitiu, dam takin. (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>282</hymn_number>
</song>